flowchart TD
    A[run_liquibase.bat / .sh] --> B[read config/<os>/<db>.conf]
    B --> C[validate liquibase + jdbc driver]
    C --> D[java -jar liquibase<br/>--changeLogFile]
    D --> E{master.xml?}
    E -->|schema| F[apply schema changelog]
    E -->|master_objects.xml| G[apply object changelog]
    F --> H[(Database)]
    G --> H
